==English==
===Etymology===
From the name of the inventor, [[w:Robert Atkins|Robert Atkins]].

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}
#''(with ''[[the]]'')'' A [[diet]] in which a person attempts to lose weight by reducing the intake of [[carbohydrate]]s, instead obtaining energy from [[dietary]] and stored [[fat]].
<!-- #:''I've lost ten pounds since I started the Atkins diet'' -->

====Synonyms====
*[[Atkins]]
*the [[Atkins Nutritional Approach]]

